<section id="res_ref">
  <title>ref</title>

  <para>Resource Item Reference - holds a reference to an associated <olink
      targetdoc="../../elements/resourcedata/resourceItem.xml" targetptr="res_resourceItem"
        ><code>&lt;resourceItem></code></olink> element located at the <olink
      targetdoc="../../elements/structural/file.xml" targetptr="file"><code>&lt;file></code></olink>
    level.</para>

  <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> An <olink targetdoc="../../xliff21.xml" targetptr="XMLSchema2">[XML Schema Datatypes]</olink> NMTOKEN</para> 

  <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> undefined</para>

  <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis><olink targetdoc="../../elements/resourcedata/resourceItemRef.xml" targetptr="res_resourceItemRef"><code>&lt;resourceItemRef></code></olink></para>
  
<itemizedlist>
  <title>Constraints</title>
  <listitem><para>The <link linkend="res_ref"><code>ref</code></link> attribute value <glossterm>must</glossterm> be the value of the <olink targetdoc="res_id.xml" targetptr="res_id"><code>id</code></olink> attribute of the <olink targetdoc="../../elements/resourcedata/resourceItem.xml" targetptr="res_resourceItem"><code>&lt;resourceItem></code></olink> element being referenced.</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>
  
</section>
